short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Modify YouTube thumbnails to include Sebastiaan

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension adds Sebastiaan to all of your Youtube thumbnails for added fun.
It is based upon the MrBeastify extension: https://github.com/MagicJinn/MrBeastify-Youtube
